steps.name: I have launched the application
I have successfully logged in to the Swag Labs e-commerce application
I have navigated to the Product Detail page
I am on the Product Detail page which contains detailed information about a product including the product image, product name, product description, and product price
the system displays the Product Detail page containing detailed information about a product including the product image, product name, product description, and product price

elements.name: Adding a product to the cart by pressing the Add to cart button

steps.name: I have launched the application
I have successfully logged in to the Swag Labs e-commerce application
I have navigated to the Product Detail page
I press the "Add to cart" button
the system successfully adds the product to my cart
the system changes the "Add to cart" button to "Remove"
the system notifies me about the increase in the number of items in the cart on the Cart Icon

elements.name: Removing a product from the cart by pressing the Remove button

steps.name: I have launched the application
I have successfully logged in to the Swag Labs e-commerce application
I have navigated to the Product Detail page
I have added the product to the cart
the button is in the "Remove" state
I press the "Remove" button
the system successfully removes the product from my cart
the system changes the "Remove" button to "Add to cart"
the system notifies me about the decrease in the number of items in the cart on the Cart Icon
I have launched the application
I have successfully logged in to the Swag Labs e-commerce application
I have navigated to the Product Detail page
I press the Cart Icon located at the top right corner
the system displays the Cart page containing the products I want to buy
